videos.description: The last time Notre Dame faced off against LSU was back in 1990 when Shaq lead the Tigers past the Irish. On Tuesday night the pair met again in the Maui Invitational semifinal, where T.J. Gibbs' 26 points lead Notre Dame to the final in a 92-53 win.
videos.headline: Irish earn spot in Maui Invitational Final
